data.title: Fun and Cozy Bar
data.text: May look packed from the outside because of the cumulative smokers by the entrance, bu the place has an unassumingly large "dining area" inside, which provides both space and comfort for a nice friendly bar experience. It's a cash only place with moderately-priced drinks, a gameroom and a pinball arcade. It is a lively and fun venue, but with a very limited set of options for food (even bar food). It's a nice place to hangout with friends or spend time alone. One of the few establishments in the area that close late.
